title: Grateful Dead Live at Rich Stadium on 1986-07-04
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) > KORG AudioGate 4 > FLAC 24/96; Edited & Mastered in Audacity by Joe Noel: Flac 24/96; Checksum & tags created in xACT; 24 bit to 16 bit with MusicConverter using sox-14-4-2
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw
Dupree's Diamond Blues
CC Rider
Tennessee Jed
My Brother Esau
Touch Of Gray

Set 2

Cold Rain & Snow->
Fire On The Mountain->
Samson & Delilah*->
The Wheel*->
I Need A Miracle*->
Uncle John's Band*->
Drums*->
Gimme Some Lovin'->
Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad->
Turn On Your Love Light

Encore:
U.S. Blues

*Broadcast on TV for Farm Aid. Dylan, Petty & Heartbreakers Opened.
